      "content": "wait, you think it's appendicitis? i thought you said it's fine to just numb it. how many ibuprofen and codeine should i actually take though? i have the 400mg ibuprefen and some leftover codeine tablets from last year, i don't want to take too much but i really need to sleep through this pain.",
